{
  "title": "法人の確定申告は自分でできる！初めてでも失敗しない決算・申告の全手順【完全ガイド】",
  "content": "<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>[swell_toc headline=\"目次\" display_level=\"2-3\"]</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br /></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":2} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">目次\r</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br /></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>1. [法人の確定申告を自分で行うための基礎知識](#基礎知識)</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>2. [法人決算・確定申告を自分でやる具体的手順](#具体的手順)</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:loos/cap-block {\"dataColSet\":\"col2\",\"className\":\"is-style-onborder_ttl2\"} -->\n<div class=\"swell-block-capbox cap_box is-style-onborder_ttl2\" data-colset=\"col2\">\n<div class=\"cap_box_ttl\"><span>重要ポイント</span></div>\n<div class=\"cap_box_content\">\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>3. [自力でやる際に気を付けたいポイントとリスク](#注意点)</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</div></div>\n<!-- /wp:loos/cap-block -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>4. [決算・申告を楽にするための便利ツール活用](#便利ツール)</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>5. [まとめ](#まとめ)</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<div class=\"accounting-data-chart\" style=\"margin: 1.5em 0; font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; font-weight: normal; color: #333;\">\n  <style>\n    .accounting-data-chart * {\n      box-sizing: border-box;\n    }\n    .accounting-data-chart .chart-title {\n      margin: 0 0 15px 0; \n      color: #1976D2; \n      font-size: 16px; \n      font-weight: bold;\n      text-align: center;\n    }\n    .accounting-data-chart .data-item {\n      display: flex; \n      align-items: center; \n      justify-content: space-between;\n      padding: 12px; \n      background: white; \n      border-radius: 8px; \n      box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); \n      margin-bottom: 10px;\n    }\n    @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {\n      .accounting-data-chart {\n        padding: 12px !important;\n      }\n      .accounting-data-chart .data-item {\n        padding: 10px !important;\n        font-size: 13px !important;\n      }\n    }\n  </style>\n  \n  <div style=\"padding: 15px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #E3F2FD 0%, #BBDEFB 100%); border-radius: 12px; border-left: 4px solid #1976D2;\">\n    <div class=\"chart-title\">📊 法人税申告の補助額シミュレーション</div>\n    \n    <div class=\"data-item\">\n      <div style=\"font-weight: bold; color: #1976D2; font-size: 14px;\">通常枠</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; color: #1976D2;\">適用税率1/2</div>\n    </div>\n    \n    <div class=\"data-item\">\n      <div style=\"font-weight: bold; color: #4CAF50; font-size: 14px;\">インボイス対応枠</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; color: #4CAF50;\">適用税率3/4</div>\n    </div>\n    \n    <div class=\"data-item\">\n      <div style=\"font-weight: bold; color: #FF9800; font-size: 14px;\">デジタル化基盤導入枠</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; color: #FF9800;\">適用税率3/4</div>\n    </div>\n    \n    <div style=\"margin-top: 15px; padding: 12px; background: rgba(25, 118, 210, 0.1); border-radius: 8px; border-left: 3px solid #1976D2;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 13px; color: #1976D2; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 4px;\">💡 実質負担額の例</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #555; line-height: 1.4;\">年額36万円の会計ソフトが、インボイス対応枠利用で実質9万円に！</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n[speech_balloon id=\"3\"]小規模な法人なら十分可能やで！会計ソフト使えば計算も書類作成も楽になるからな。[/speech_balloon]\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":2} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">法人の確定申告を自分で行うための基礎知識 {#基礎知識}\r</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br /></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<div class=\"accounting-calc-process\" style=\"margin: 1.5em 0;\">\n  <style>\n    .accounting-calc-process * {\n      box-sizing: border-box;\n    }\n    @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {\n      .accounting-calc-process {\n        padding: 12px !important;\n      }\n      .accounting-calc-process .calc-step {\n        padding: 10px !important;\n        font-size: 12px !important;\n      }\n    }\n  </style>\n  \n  <div style=\"padding: 15px; background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 12px; border-left: 4px solid #4CAF50;\">\n    <div style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 15px; color: #2E7D32; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold;\">🧮 法人確定申告の流れ</div>\n    \n    <div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px;\">\n      <div class=\"calc-step\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 12px; background: white; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\">\n        <div style=\"width: 32px; height: 32px; background: #4CAF50; color: white; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: bold; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0; font-size: 14px;\">1</div>\n        <div style=\"flex: 1;\">\n          <div style=\"font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 4px; font-size: 14px;\">年間取引データの整理</div>\n          <div style=\"font-size: 13px; color: #666;\">国税庁のe-Taxまたは書面で申請</div>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; color: #4CAF50; min-width: 80px; text-align: right;\">必須</div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"calc-step\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 12px; background: white; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\">\n        <div style=\"width: 32px; height: 32px; background: #2196F3; color: white; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: bold; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0; font-size: 14px;\">2</div>\n        <div style=\"flex: 1;\">\n          <div style=\"font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 4px; font-size: 14px;\">決算整理と申告書作成</div>\n          <div style=\"font-size: 13px; color: #666;\">適格請求書対応の設定と確認</div>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; color: #2196F3; min-width: 80px; text-align: right;\">1日</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    \n    <div style=\"margin-top: 15px; padding: 15px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF9800 0%, #FF5722 100%); color: white; border-radius: 8px; text-align: center;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 5px;\">対応完了で得られる効果</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold;\">経理業務60%削減</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n[speech_balloon id=\"3\"]小規模な法人なら十分可能やで！会計ソフト使えば計算も書類作成も楽になるからな。[/speech_balloon]\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">法人決算と確定申告の流れをおさらい\r</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>法人の決算・申告は以下の流れで進みます：</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>決算日 → 決算作業（2ヶ月以内） → 申告書作成 → 申告・納税 → 完了</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:loos/cap-block {\"dataColSet\":\"col2\",\"className\":\"is-style-onborder_ttl2\"} -->\n<div class=\"swell-block-capbox cap_box is-style-onborder_ttl2\" data-colset=\"col2\">\n<div class=\"cap_box_ttl\"><span>重要ポイント</span></div>\n<div class=\"cap_box_content\">\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>重要なポイント：</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</div></div>\n<!-- /wp:loos/cap-block -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>何をもって「完了」となるかを明確にしておくことで、作業の見通しが立てやすくなります。</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n[speech_balloon id=\"5\"]法人の確定申告って自分でできるものなんですか？[/speech_balloon]\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">自分で行う場合に必要なもの（知識・ツール・時間）\r</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>自力申告に必要な準備は以下の通りです：</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:loos/cap-block {\"dataColSet\":\"col2\",\"className\":\"is-style-onborder_ttl2\"} -->\n<div class=\"swell-block-capbox cap_box is-style-onborder_ttl2\" data-colset=\"col2\">\n<div class=\"cap_box_ttl\"><span>重要ポイント</span></div>\n<div class=\"cap_box_content\">\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>✅ 必要な知識</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</div></div>\n<!-- /wp:loos/cap-block -->\n\n<!-- wp:loos/cap-block {\"dataColSet\":\"col2\",\"className\":\"is-style-onborder_ttl2\"} -->\n<div class=\"swell-block-capbox cap_box is-style-onborder_ttl2\" data-colset=\"col2\">\n<div class=\"cap_box_ttl\"><span>重要ポイント</span></div>\n<div class=\"cap_box_content\">\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>✅ 必要なツール</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</div></div>\n<!-- /wp:loos/cap-block -->\n\n<!-- wp:loos/cap-block {\"dataColSet\":\"col2\",\"className\":\"is-style-onborder_ttl2\"} -->\n<div class=\"swell-block-capbox cap_box is-style-onborder_ttl2\" data-colset=\"col2\">\n<div class=\"cap_box_ttl\"><span>重要ポイント</span></div>\n<div class=\"cap_box_content\">\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>✅ 必要な時間</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</div></div>\n<!-- /wp:loos/cap-block -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>これらが揃えば、自分でも申告は十分可能です。</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">税理士に依頼する場合との違い・メリット比較\r</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:loos/cap-block {\"dataColSet\":\"col2\",\"className\":\"is-style-onborder_ttl2\"} -->\n<div class=\"swell-block-capbox cap_box is-style-onborder_ttl2\" data-colset=\"col2\">\n<div class=\"cap_box_ttl\"><span>重要ポイント</span></div>\n<div class=\"cap_box_content\">\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>自分でやるメリット：</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</div></div>\n<!-- /wp:loos/cap-block -->\n\n<!-- wp:loos/cap-block {\"dataColSet\":\"col2\",\"className\":\"is-style-onborder_ttl2\"} -->\n<div class=\"swell-block-capbox cap_box is-style-onborder_ttl2\" data-colset=\"col2\">\n<div class=\"cap_box_ttl\"><span>重要ポイント</span></div>\n<div class=\"cap_box_content\">\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>税理士依頼のメリット：</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</div></div>\n<!-- /wp:loos/cap-block -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>小規模法人であれば、コスト重視で自力申告にチャレンジする価値は十分にあります。</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":2} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">法人決算・確定申告を自分でやる具体的手順 {#具体的手順}\r</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br /></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:loos/step {\"className\":\"is-style-default\"} -->\n<div class=\"swell-block-step is-style-default\" data-num-style=\"circle\">\n<!-- wp:loos/step-item {\"stepLabel\":\"STEP\"} -->\n<div class=\"swell-block-step__item\">\n<div class=\"swell-block-step__number u-bg-main\"><span class=\"__label\">STEP</span><span class=\"__num\">1</span></div>\n<div class=\"swell-block-step__title u-fz-l\">年間取引データの整理</div>\n<div class=\"swell-block-step__body\">\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>帳簿データを整理して試算表を作成します</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</div></div>\n<!-- /wp:loos/step-item -->\n<!-- wp:loos/step-item {\"stepLabel\":\"STEP\"} -->\n<div class=\"swell-block-step__item\">\n<div class=\"swell-block-step__number u-bg-main\"><span class=\"__label\">STEP</span><span class=\"__num\">2</span></div>\n<div class=\"swell-block-step__title u-fz-l\">決算整理と申告書作成</div>\n<div class=\"swell-block-step__body\">\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>決算整理仕訳を行い、法人税申告書を作成します</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</div></div>\n<!-- /wp:loos/step-item -->\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:loos/step -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">① 日々の取引を整理し試算表を作成\r</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:loos/cap-block {\"dataColSet\":\"col2\",\"className\":\"is-style-onborder_ttl2\"} -->\n<div class=\"swell-block-capbox cap_box is-style-onborder_ttl2\" data-colset=\"col2\">\n<div class=\"cap_box_ttl\"><span>重要ポイント</span></div>\n<div class=\"cap_box_content\">\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>STEP 1/5</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</div></div>\n<!-- /wp:loos/cap-block -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>まず、1年間の取引データをまとめて試算表を作成します。</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:loos/cap-block {\"dataColSet\":\"col2\",\"className\":\"is-style-onborder_ttl2\"} -->\n<div class=\"swell-block-capbox cap_box is-style-onborder_ttl2\" data-colset=\"col2\">\n<div class=\"cap_box_ttl\"><span>重要ポイント</span></div>\n<div class=\"cap_box_content\">\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>やること：</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</div></div>\n<!-- /wp:loos/cap-block -->\n\n<!-- wp:loos/cap-block {\"dataColSet\":\"col2\",\"className\":\"is-style-onborder_ttl2\"} -->\n<div class=\"swell-block-capbox cap_box is-style-onborder_ttl2\" data-colset=\"col2\">\n<div class=\"cap_box_ttl\"><span>重要ポイント</span></div>\n<div class=\"cap_box_content\">\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>試算表とは？: 各勘定科目の残高を一覧にした表のこと。これを見れば会社の財務状況が分かります。</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</div></div>\n<!-- /wp:loos/cap-block -->\n\n<!-- wp:loos/cap-block {\"dataColSet\":\"col2\",\"className\":\"is-style-onborder_ttl2\"} -->\n<div class=\"swell-block-capbox cap_box is-style-onborder_ttl2\" data-colset=\"col2\">\n<div class=\"cap_box_ttl\"><span>重要ポイント</span></div>\n<div class=\"cap_box_content\">\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>便利な方法：</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</div></div>\n<!-- /wp:loos/cap-block -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">② 決算整理仕訳と決算書類（貸借対照表・PLなど）作成\r</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:loos/cap-block {\"dataColSet\":\"col2\",\"className\":\"is-style-onborder_ttl2\"} -->\n<div class=\"swell-block-capbox cap_box is-style-onborder_ttl2\" data-colset=\"col2\">\n<div class=\"cap_box_ttl\"><span>重要ポイント</span></div>\n<div class=\"cap_box_content\">\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>STEP 2/5</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</div></div>\n<!-- /wp:loos/cap-block -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>決算特有の処理を行い、正式な決算書を作成します。</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:loos/cap-block {\"dataColSet\":\"col2\",\"className\":\"is-style-onborder_ttl2\"} -->\n<div class=\"swell-block-capbox cap_box is-style-onborder_ttl2\" data-colset=\"col2\">\n<div class=\"cap_box_ttl\"><span>重要ポイント</span></div>\n<div class=\"cap_box_content\">\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>主な決算整理事項：</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</div></div>\n<!-- /wp:loos/cap-block -->\n\n<!-- wp:loos/cap-block {\"dataColSet\":\"col2\",\"className\":\"is-style-onborder_ttl2\"} -->\n<div class=\"swell-block-capbox cap_box is-style-onborder_ttl2\" data-colset=\"col2\">\n<div class=\"cap_box_ttl\"><span>重要ポイント</span></div>\n<div class=\"cap_box_content\">\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>1. 減価償却：固定資産の価値減少を計上</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</div></div>\n<!-- /wp:loos/cap-block -->\n\n<!-- wp:loos/cap-block {\"dataColSet\":\"col2\",\"className\":\"is-style-onborder_ttl2\"} -->\n<div class=\"swell-block-capbox cap_box is-style-onborder_ttl2\" data-colset=\"col2\">\n<div class=\"cap_box_ttl\"><span>重要ポイント</span></div>\n<div class=\"cap_box_content\">\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>2. 売上原価算定：期首在庫 + 当期仕入 - 期末在庫</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</div></div>\n<!-- /wp:loos/cap-block -->\n\n<!-- wp:loos/cap-block {\"dataColSet\":\"col2\",\"className\":\"is-style-onborder_ttl2\"} -->\n<div class=\"swell-block-capbox cap_box is-style-onborder_ttl2\" data-colset=\"col2\">\n<div class=\"cap_box_ttl\"><span>重要ポイント</span></div>\n<div class=\"cap_box_content\">\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>3. 未払費用：当期分だが翌期支払いの経費を計上</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</div></div>\n<!-- /wp:loos/cap-block -->\n\n<!-- wp:loos/cap-block {\"dataColSet\":\"col2\",\"className\":\"is-style-onborder_ttl2\"} -->\n<div class=\"swell-block-capbox cap_box is-style-onborder_ttl2\" data-colset=\"col2\">\n<div class=\"cap_box_ttl\"><span>重要ポイント</span></div>\n<div class=\"cap_box_content\">\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>4. 前払費用：翌期分を当期から除外</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</div></div>\n<!-- /wp:loos/cap-block -->\n\n<!-- wp:loos/cap-block {\"dataColSet\":\"col2\",\"className\":\"is-style-onborder_ttl2\"} -->\n<div class=\"swell-block-capbox cap_box is-style-onborder_ttl2\" data-colset=\"col2\">\n<div class=\"cap_box_ttl\"><span>重要ポイント</span></div>\n<div class=\"cap_box_content\">\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>該当がない項目は飛ばしてOK！</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</div></div>\n<!-- /wp:loos/cap-block -->\n\n<!-- wp:loos/cap-block {\"dataColSet\":\"col2\",\"className\":\"is-style-onborder_ttl2\"} -->\n<div class=\"swell-block-capbox cap_box is-style-onborder_ttl2\" data-colset=\"col2\">\n<div class=\"cap_box_ttl\"><span>重要ポイント</span></div>\n<div class=\"cap_box_content\">\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>作成する決算書：</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</div></div>\n<!-- /wp:loos/cap-block -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>会計ソフトを使っていれば、決算整理仕訳を入力するだけで自動作成されます。</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n[speech_balloon id=\"3\"]小規模な法人なら十分可能やで！会計ソフト使えば計算も書類作成も楽になるからな。[/speech_balloon]\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">③ 法人税申告書類の作成（別表の埋め方）\r</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:loos/cap-block {\"dataColSet\":\"col2\",\"className\":\"is-style-onborder_ttl2\"} -->\n<div class=\"swell-block-capbox cap_box is-style-onborder_ttl2\" data-colset=\"col2\">\n<div class=\"cap_box_ttl\"><span>重要ポイント</span></div>\n<div class=\"cap_box_content\">\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>STEP 3/5 ⚠️ 最も重要な工程</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</div></div>\n<!-- /wp:loos/cap-block -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>決算書ができたら、法人税申告書（別表）を作成します。</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:loos/cap-block {\"dataColSet\":\"col2\",\"className\":\"is-style-onborder_ttl2\"} -->\n<div class=\"swell-block-capbox cap_box is-style-onborder_ttl2\" data-colset=\"col2\">\n<div class=\"cap_box_ttl\"><span>重要ポイント</span></div>\n<div class=\"cap_box_content\">\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>主要な別表：</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</div></div>\n<!-- /wp:loos/cap-block -->\n\n<!-- wp:loos/cap-block {\"dataColSet\":\"col2\",\"className\":\"is-style-onborder_ttl2\"} -->\n<div class=\"swell-block-capbox cap_box is-style-onborder_ttl2\" data-colset=\"col2\">\n<div class=\"cap_box_ttl\"><span>重要ポイント</span></div>\n<div class=\"cap_box_content\">\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>基本的な税務調整例：</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</div></div>\n<!-- /wp:loos/cap-block -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>会計上の利益：100万円</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>+ 交際費超過額：10万円（損金不算入）</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>+ 減価償却超過額：5万円</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>= 課税所得：115万円</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:loos/cap-block {\"dataColSet\":\"col2\",\"className\":\"is-style-onborder_ttl2\"} -->\n<div class=\"swell-block-capbox cap_box is-style-onborder_ttl2\" data-colset=\"col2\">\n<div class=\"cap_box_ttl\"><span>重要ポイント</span></div>\n<div class=\"cap_box_content\">\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>💡 ポイント：</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</div></div>\n<!-- /wp:loos/cap-block -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">④ 税務署・県税事務所等への申告書提出（電子申告の方法）\r</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:loos/cap-block {\"dataColSet\":\"col2\",\"className\":\"is-style-onborder_ttl2\"} -->\n<div class=\"swell-block-capbox cap_box is-style-onborder_ttl2\" data-colset=\"col2\">\n<div class=\"cap_box_ttl\"><span>重要ポイント</span></div>\n<div class=\"cap_box_content\">\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>STEP 4/5</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</div></div>\n<!-- /wp:loos/cap-block -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>申告書が完成したら、期限内に提出します。</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:loos/cap-block {\"dataColSet\":\"col2\",\"className\":\"is-style-onborder_ttl2\"} -->\n<div class=\"swell-block-capbox cap_box is-style-onborder_ttl2\" data-colset=\"col2\">\n<div class=\"cap_box_ttl\"><span>重要ポイント</span></div>\n<div class=\"cap_box_content\">\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>提出方法は2つ：</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</div></div>\n<!-- /wp:loos/cap-block -->\n\n<!-- wp:loos/cap-block {\"dataColSet\":\"col2\",\"className\":\"is-style-onborder_ttl2\"} -->\n<div class=\"swell-block-capbox cap_box is-style-onborder_ttl2\" data-colset=\"col2\">\n<div class=\"cap_box_ttl\"><span>重要ポイント</span></div>\n<div class=\"cap_box_content\">\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>1. 窓口・郵送提出：従来の方法</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</div></div>\n<!-- /wp:loos/cap-block -->\n\n<!-- wp:loos/cap-block {\"dataColSet\":\"col2\",\"className\":\"is-style-onborder_ttl2\"} -->\n<div class=\"swell-block-capbox cap_box is-style-onborder_ttl2\" data-colset=\"col2\">\n<div class=\"cap_box_ttl\"><span>重要ポイント</span></div>\n<div class=\"cap_box_content\">\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>